item.description:
Finding auto layout information is difficult. The steps below pin a navigation bar to the top of the screen for all iOS devices.
{% img center /images/constraints.gif %}
Steps  Make sure &ldquo;Navigation Bar&rdquo; is selected on the left menu Click the &ldquo;Pin&rdquo; button on the bottom right corner Click the top, left and right constraints Click the Height constraint Add the 4 contraints  The above steps &ldquo;pin&rdquo; the navigation bar object to the top of the view and stretch the navigation bar to the sides of the view.
